CAPTURE THE FLAG!  v1.3  Trophy Winner!
One of the most reviewed shareware games
(by major media) ever!  See AWARD.DOC for 
unabridged reviews.  Dash through opponent's
beautifully detailed terrain in a desperate
race to capture their flag before they 
capture yours.  Analyze your team's skills,
develop tactics and deploy your teammates 
using natural cover to intercept and capture
the opposition's raiders.  640K, VGA, & 286+
